WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.362 --> 00:00:10.077
For full-auto PC control of trains, 
this double-crossing is a key point. 

00:00:16.669 --> 00:00:30.500
During Amtrack is entering main yard, 
a empty coal waits. 

00:00:50.385 --> 00:01:05.451
Before moving empty coal train, 
double-stack train departs to loop section. 

00:02:20.239 --> 00:02:28.287
Then, every signal is set to Red. 

00:02:30.239 --> 00:02:45.287
Then, empty coal train arrives at main yard. 

00:03:00.377 --> 00:03:15.737
Depending on the setup of PC control, 
each train can start 
when some departure conditions are met. 

00:03:40.377 --> 00:03:55.737
Amtrack is arriving but, before that, 
Double-stack train departs. 

